    "body": "Remove duplicate useLoadingBarVisibility() from TopBar.\n\nBoth SearchSidebar and TopBar independently subscribed to the same Onyx keys (PERSISTED_REQUESTS, PERSISTED_ONGOING_REQUESTS). Now TopBar receives the value via prop; callers that relied on the internal fallback (BaseSidebarScreen, InitialSettingsPage, WorkspacesListPage) pass it explicitly.\n\n<details><summary>Issue Owner</summary>Current Issue Owner: @jmusial</details>\n<details><summary>Upwork Automation - Do Not Edit</summary>\n    <ul>\n        <li>Upwork Job URL: https://www.upwork.com/jobs/~022033574600145585267</li>\n        <li>Upwork Job ID: 2033574600145585267</li>\n        <li>Last Price Increase: 2026-03-16</li>\n    </ul>\n</details>",
